| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1084 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d645051d-3bc5-5ff9-9957-2d5b9cbe38e6"
